(1, 'Meetings, Incentives, Conferences, and Exhibitions', 'Meetings, Incentives, Conferences, and Exhibitions', '<p>Sedang merencanakan Conference atau Meetings di Eropa? Your Private Europe (YPE) siap membantu sebagai partner di negara tujuan MICE Anda. Dengan pengalaman kami dan kemampuan mendengarkan kebutuhan klien, kami yakin bisa memberikan solusi terbaik untuk acara bisnis Anda. Mulai dari venue hingga detail kecil seperti refreshment dan audio-visual, semua kami urus dengan rapi dan efisien.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kami selalu mengadopsi cara kerja yang kolaboratif dan terstruktur. Artinya, kami nggak cuma membantu memilih lokasi, tapi juga memastikan seluruh proses dari awal sampai akhir berjalan mulus. Dari agenda planning, eksekusi acara, hingga kebutuhan teknis seperti conference room dan AV system, semua di-manage secara profesional dan detail. Anda cukup fokus di Meeting, sementara kami yang urus sisanya.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tak hanya itu, kami juga handle seluruh transportasi dan akomodasi. Kalau ada kebutuhan logistik tambahan? Jangan khawatir, YPE sudah siap dari awal untuk menghadapi berbagai skenario, termasuk permintaan mendadak. Fleksibilitas adalah kekuatan kami—apa pun yang Anda butuhkan, kami siap menyesuaikan.</p> \r\n\r\n<p>Kami selalu melihat acara Anda secara end-to-end. Jadi, setiap aspek dirancang dan dieksekusi dengan sempurna. Kami paham bahwa event Anda adalah representasi brand dan misi perusahaan, jadi kami pastikan semuanya sesuai standar tinggi. Dari venue selection, transportation, hingga F&B, semuanya ditangani secara detail.</p>', '<p>Planning a Conference or Meeting in Europe?\r\nYour Private Europe (YPE) is here to assist as your partner in your MICE destination. With our experience and our ability to listen to clients\' needs, we’re confident we can provide the best solutions for your business event. From venue selection to small details like refreshments and audiovisual requirements, we handle everything with precision and efficiency.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We always adopt a collaborative and structured approach. This means we don’t just help choose the location—we ensure the entire process runs smoothly from start to finish. From agenda planning, event execution, to technical requirements such as conference rooms and AV systems, everything is managed professionally and meticulously. You can focus on the meeting, while we take care of the rest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Moreover, we handle all transportation and accommodation. Need extra logistical support? Don’t worry, YPE is ready from the start to manage various scenarios, including last-minute requests. Flexibility is our strength—whatever you need, we’re ready to adapt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We approach your event in an end-to-end manner. Every aspect is designed and executed to perfection. We understand that your event represents your brand and company mission, so we ensure everything meets the highest standards. From venue selection, transportation, to F&B, we take care of every detail.</p>'),
(3, 'Event Management & Logistics', 'Event Management & Logistics', '<p>Merencanakan event di Eropa? Nggak usah pusing. Di Your Private Europe (YPE), kami siap bantu Anda mulai dari perencanaan hingga eksekusi. Kami paham setiap detail penting, apapun jenis acaranya—entah itu Gala Dinner, Brand/Product Launching, atau Company Party—kami urus semuanya dari awal sampai akhir.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kami percaya pada cara kerja end-to-end, di mana setiap aspek event Anda kami lihat secara menyeluruh. Mulai dari venue, akomodasi, hingga pengaturan transportasi dan logistik, semua dikelola secara detail dan profesional. Kami juga menyediakan event staffing yang berpengalaman, siap mengelola acara Anda dengan mulus.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Butuh F&B yang sesuai dengan tema acara? Kami siap. Mau ide gifts & teasers untuk para tamu? Kami juga punya banyak opsi. Dengan pengalaman kami, acara Anda akan terasa seamless dan bebas dari kendala.</p>', '<p>Planning an Event in Europe? Don’t Worry.\r\nAt Your Private Europe (YPE), we’re here to assist you from planning to execution. We understand that every detail matters, no matter the type of event—whether it\'s a Gala Dinner, Brand/Product Launch, or Company Party—we handle everything from start to finish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We believe in an end-to-end approach, where every aspect of your event is carefully considered. From the venue, accommodations, transportation, to logistics, everything is managed with attention to detail and professionalism. We also provide experienced event staffing, ready to ensure your event runs smoothly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Need F&B options that match your event’s theme? We’ve got you covered. Looking for gift ideas and teasers for your guests? We have plenty of options. With our experience, your event will be seamless and free from any issues.</p>');

