(1, 'Layanan Limousine, Fotografi, Jastip, dan Catering | Your Private Europe', 'Luxury Services | Catering, Limousines & More | Your Private Europe', 'Nikmati perjalanan tanpa beban di Eropa dengan layanan limousine, fotografi, jastip, dan catering dari Your Private Europe. Buat momen di Eropa lebih berkesan.', 'Complete your European experience with our additional services, including catering, limousine charters, professional photographers, and more.', 'Pelayanan Kami Lainnya', 'Other Services', 'Buat Kunjungan Anda Di Eropa Lebih Lengkap & Spesial ', 'Make Your Visit In Europe More Memorable & Special', 'limousine.jpg', 'Limousine Charter: Tampil Wah Di Momen Luar Biasa', 'Limousine Charter: Arrive in Style for Extraordinary Moments', '<p>Ketika kamu diundang ke gala event, red carpet premiere, atau pesta paling eksklusif di Eropa, hadir dengan mobil biasa jelas bukan opsinya. Kamu adalah pusat perhatian, dan setiap detail harus <strong>on point</strong> termasuk kendaraan yang membawamu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Di Your Private Europe, kami menyediakan layanan <strong>Limousine Charter</strong> yang dirancang khusus untuk orang-orang sepertimu—super <strong>VIP</strong> yang mengutamakan gaya, kenyamanan, dan prestise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mobil yang kamu kendarai bukan cuma alat transportasi; itu adalah perpanjangan dari kehadiranmu. <strong>Limousine</strong> kami dirancang untuk menciptakan kesan yang tak terlupakan saat kamu tiba di venue:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>-Desain eksterior yang mewah dan elegan. </br>\r\n-Fasilitas interior premium seperti custom leather seating, minibar pribadi, dan sistem hiburan berkelas. </br>\r\n-Pengemudi profesional berpengalaman yang siap memberikan layanan sempurna.</strong></p>', '<p>When you’re invited to a gala event, a red-carpet premiere, or Europe’s most exclusive parties, arriving in an ordinary car simply isn’t an option. You’re the center of attention, and every detail must be <strong>flawless</strong>—including the vehicle that brings you there.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Your Private Europe (YPE), we offer bespoke <strong>Limousine Charter</strong> services tailored for individuals like you—super VIPs who value style, comfort, and prestige.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Your Private Europe, we offer <strong>Limousine Charter</strong> services designed for individuals like you—super <strong>VIPs</strong> who value style, comfort, and prestige.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The car you arrive in is more than just transportation; it’s an extension of your presence. Our <strong>limousines</strong> are designed to leave a lasting impression when you step out at the venue, featuring:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>- Luxurious and elegant exterior design.</strong></p>  \r\n<p><strong>- Premium interior amenities including custom leather seating, a personal minibar, and high-end entertainment systems.</strong></p>  \r\n<p><strong>- Experienced professional chauffeurs committed to providing impeccable service.</strong></p>\r\n'),
(2, 'Layanan Fotografi, Jastip, dan Catering | Your Private Europe', 'Photography, Shopping Assistant, and Catering Services | Your Private Europe', 'Nikmati perjalanan tanpa beban di Eropa dengan layanan fotografi, jastip, dan catering dari Your Private Europe. Buat momen di Eropa lebih berkesan.', 'Enjoy a hassle-free journey in Europe with photography, shopping assistant (Jastip), and catering services from Your Private Europe. Make your moments in Europe more memorable.', 'Pelayanan Kami Lainnya', 'Other Services', 'Buat Kunjungan Anda Di Eropa Lebih Lengkap & Spesial ', 'Make Your Visit In Europe More Memorable & Special', 'photograph.jpg', 'Fotografer Professional', 'Professional Photographer', '<p>Abadikan momen <strong>liburan Anda di Eropa</strong> dengan foto professional yang sempurna!</p>\r\n<p>Kami menyediakan <strong>layanan fotografer professional</strong> selama liburan Anda di Eropa, yang akan membantu Anda mendokumentasikan <strong>kenangan-kenangan berharga</strong> dengan pasangan, keluarga dan orang-orang yang Anda cintai lainnya.</p>\r\n<p>Fotografer berpengalaman kami sangat mengenal tempat-tempat di Eropa yang cocok untuk mengabadikan momen-momen liburan Anda, dan membuat setiap <strong>pengalaman Anda menjadi tak terlupakan!</strong></p>', '<p>Capture your <strong>holiday moments in Europe</strong> with beautifully-shot professional photos!</p>\r\n<p>We provide <strong>professional photographer services</strong> during your vacation in Europe, which will allow you to document <strong>precious memories</strong> with your spouse, family and loved ones.</p>\r\n<p>Our experienced photographers are very familiar with places in Europe that are suitable for capturing your holiday moments, and to make your <strong>experiences unforgettable!</strong></p>'),
(3, 'Layanan Fotografi, Jastip, dan Catering | Your Private Europe', 'Photography, Shopping Assistant, and Catering Services | Your Private Europe', 'Nikmati perjalanan tanpa beban di Eropa dengan layanan fotografi, jastip, dan catering dari Your Private Europe. Buat momen di Eropa lebih berkesan.', 'Enjoy a hassle-free journey in Europe with photography, shopping assistant (Jastip), and catering services from Your Private Europe. Make your moments in Europe more memorable.', 'Pelayanan Kami Lainnya', 'Other Services', 'Buat Kunjungan Anda Di Eropa Lebih Lengkap & Spesial ', 'Make Your Visit In Europe More Memorable & Special', 'catering_service.jpg', 'Catering Masakan Indonesia', 'Catering Service Indonesian Food', '<p>Kangen dengan makanan asli Indonesia selama kunjungan Anda di Eropa?</p>\r\n<p>Kami menyediakan <strong>catering masakan Indonesia</strong> yang bisa Anda pesan dengan <strong>paket tour Anda</strong> dengan kami. Nikmati makanan kesukaan Anda untuk <strong>piknik di waktu makan siang</strong>, atau <strong>waktu makan malam bareng</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>Mulai dari <strong>snacks kecil</strong> sampai makanan besar, semua masakan diolah secara&nbsp;<em>home-made</em> oleh <strong>orang-orang Indonesia yang tinggal di Eropa</strong>, dan sangat terjamin secara <strong>rasa dan kualitas</strong>.</p>\r\n', '<p>Do you miss eating authentic Indonesian food during your visit to Europe?</p>\r\n<p>We provide catering service with Indonesian food that you can order with your tour package with us. Enjoy your favorite food for a picnic at lunch or dinner.</p>\r\n<p class=\" translation-block\">From small snacks to large meals, all dishes are <em> home-made </em> by Indonesians living in Europe, and are guaranteed in terms of taste and quality.</p>'),
(6, 'Layanan Fotografi, Jastip, dan Catering | Your Private Europe', 'Photography, Shopping Assistant, and Catering Services | Your Private Europe', 'Nikmati perjalanan tanpa beban di Eropa dengan layanan fotografi, jastip, dan catering dari Your Private Europe. Buat momen di Eropa lebih berkesan.', 'Enjoy a hassle-free journey in Europe with photography, shopping assistant (Jastip), and catering services from Your Private Europe. Make your moments in Europe more memorable.', 'Pelayanan Kami Lainnya', 'Other Services', 'Buat Kunjungan Anda Di Eropa Lebih Lengkap & Spesial ', 'Make Your Visit In Europe More Memorable & Special', 'jastip.jpg', 'Pengiriman Barang (Jastip) ', 'Goods Delivery', '<p><strong>Anda ingin berbelanja atau membeli barang di Eropa,</strong> tapi tidak bisa membawa semuanya pulang ke Indonesia?</p>\r\n<p>Jangan kuatir, kami siap membantu Anda! <strong>Kami menyediakan pelayanan pengiriman barang dan jastip ke Indonesia dari Eropa dengan harga yang kompetitif.</strong> Anda tidak perlu kuatir lagi dengan <em>bagage overweight&nbsp;</em>atau kerepotan membawa barang bawaan Anda.</p>\r\n<p>Mulai dari barang mewah, alat-alat industri atau souvenir-souvenir khusus, <strong>kami menjamin keamanan barang Anda sampai dengan tujuan di Indonesia</strong>.</p>', '<p><strong>Do you want to go on shopping spree or buy goods in Europe,</strong> but can\'t bring them all back to Indonesia?</p>\r\n<p class=\" translation-block\">Don\'t worry, we\'ve got you covered! <strong>We provide goods delivery services from Europe to Indonesia at competitive price.</strong> You don\'t need to worry anymore with <em>bagage overweight</em> or the hassle of carrying your heavy luggage.</p>\r\n<p>From luxury goods, industrial tools to special souvenirs, <strong>we guarantee the safety of your goods until their destination in Indonesia.</strong></p>');

