(1, 'Layanan Perjalanan VIP di Eropa | Your Private Europe ', 'VIP Travel Services in Europe | Your Private Europe', 'Ingin jalan-jalan di Eropa dengan layanan VIP? Kami bisa atur semuanya, mulai dari supir berbahasa Indonesia hingga pesawat private jet. Hubungi kami.', 'Enjoy bespoke VIP travel in Europe. From luxury limousine charters to exclusive experiences, Your Private Europe curates premium services.', 'VIP SERVICES', 'Kemewahan Liburan di Eropa yang Sebenarnya', 'The True Luxury of a Private European Holiday', 'Bayangin ini: Kamu lagi di Monaco, nonton F1 dari pit lane VIP, lalu besoknya jet pribadi udah siap bawa kamu ke Ibiza buat pesta sampai pagi. Sounds like a dream? Di Your Private Europe, ini cuma salah satu dari banyak pengalaman wisata Eropa yang bisa kami wujudkan.', 'Imagine this: You\'re in Monaco, watching the F1 Grand Prix from a VIP pit lane. The next day, a private jet is ready to whisk you away to Ibiza for an unforgettable night of revelry. Sounds like a dream? At Your Private Europe, this is just one of many extraordinary experiences we can bring to life.', 'vip-services'),
(2, 'Private Tour di Eropa | Travelling Lebih Bebas | Your Private Europe', 'Tailored Europe Private Trip & Tours | Your Private Europe', 'Ingin pengalaman travelling di Eropa yang lebih personal? Atur sendiri destinasi, aktivitas, dan tanggal keberangkatanmu  dengan Your Private Europe.', 'Experience the best of Europe with custom private trips. Flexible itineraries, luxury services, and unforgettable tours designed just for you.', 'PRIVATE TOUR', 'Private Tour Eropa: Liburan Sesuai Gaya Kamu', 'Private European Tour: A Vacation Tailored to Your Style', 'Pernah nggak kebayang bisa liburan ke Eropa dengan itinerary yang benar-benar dibuat sesuai kebutuhanmu? \r\n\r\nKebanyakan perusahaan tur mungkin menawarkan private tour, tapi sering kali mereka tetap punya jadwal tetap, rute standar, dan pengalaman yang terbatas. \r\n\r\nDi Your Private Europe, pengalaman liburanmu nggak cuma \"private\", tapi fully customised. Artinya, setiap detil perjalanan kami bangun berdasarkan siapa kamu dan apa yang kamu inginkan.', 'Ever Dreamed of Traveling to Europe with an Itinerary Tailored Just for You?\r\n\r\nMost tour companies may offer private tours, but they often come with fixed schedules, standard routes, and limited experiences.\r\n\r\nAt Your Private Europe, your vacation isn’t just “private”—it’s fully customized. Every detail of your journey is crafted based on who you are and what you want.', 'private-tour'),
(3, 'MICE | Event Management di Eropa | Your Private Europe', 'Destination Events & Corporate Solutions | Your Private Europe', 'Buat event di Eropa? Your Private Europe sudah berpengalaman dalam merencanakan hingga mengatur logistic untuk berbagai event MICE di Eropa.', 'Plan seamless corporate events in Europe with Your Private Europe. From venues to logistics, we deliver flawless destination event experiences.', 'DESTINATION EVENTS', 'Partner Terbaik untuk Event Perusahaan Anda', 'The Best Partner for Your Corporate Event', 'Melalui layanan MICE kami. Dari konferensi besar hingga acara perusahaan kecil, kami menyediakan fasilitas dan layanan yang dibutuhkan untuk kesuksesan acara Anda', 'Through our MICE services. From large conferences to small corporate events, we provide the facilities and services needed for the success of your event', 'destination-event'),
(4, 'Kerjasama Travel ke Eropa untuk Agent & Corporate | YPE', 'Trusted & Reliable Europe Tour Partner for Agents | Your Private Europe', 'Your Private Europe adalah mitra terpercaya untuk travel agent dan perusahaan yang merencanakan perjalanan atau acara bisnis di Eropa. ', 'Partner with Your Private Europe for premium travel solutions. Custom tours, group trips, and seamless travel services tailored to your clients.', 'TOUR AGENT', 'Layanan B2B Travel Agent & Corporate', 'B2B Travel Agent & Corporate Travel Services', 'Sedang mencari partner travel yang bisa urus segala kebutuhan klien atau perusahaan Anda? Your Private Europe (YPE) adalah jawabannya. Sebagai solusi lengkap untuk perjalanan di Eropa, kami siap memenuhi semua kebutuhan travel Anda, mulai dari tours, akomodasi, hingga event management.\r\n', 'Looking for a reliable travel partner to handle all your clients’ or company’s travel needs? Your Private Europe (YPE) is your ultimate solution. From tours and accommodations to event management, we provide comprehensive services for seamless travel experiences across Europe.', 'tour-agent');

